reviewText: I love Rollie Polie Olie. Fast shipping also!
The options to play the cartoons are so confusing!

My Granddaughters were very happy to meet Rolie Polie Olie & share his adventures. (Their Mom & Dad liked him too. They came to visit this summer from Long Island, NY & brought this CD in the car to watch on the trip. Thank you for making 2 little girls happy. A+A+A+
When I used to be a nanny - this was on the Disney channel.  The kids LOVED this show!!!  When my niece & nephew were born...I knew I had to find these videos!!!  ALL ARE SPECIAL & WONDERFUL!!!  :)
